== Overview ==
''Cargodest'' is a system where cargo decides where it wishes to go and not the player (by sending vehicles somewhere). This greatly increases the challenge and detail of the game and frankly, it's more fun and realistic as well. There have been a number of attempts at integrating this feature into OpenTTD and we're nearly there meanwhile. This page deals with some of the technical and gameplay details of ''cargodest'' and provides a short manual on how to use it.

